(6, 3, 81, 'PETRA 1 DAY TOUR', 'Visit the ancient city of Petra on a full-day excursion from Sharm El Sheikh. First you will sail from Taba to Aqaba in luxury and then drive to Petra, where you will visit the most popular attraction in Jordan.', '<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding: 0px 15px; float: left; width: 750px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-size-adjust: none;\">\r\n<div class=\"tab_view\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-size-adjust: none;\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-size-adjust: none;\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"Itinerary\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-size-adjust: none; visibility: visible; opacity: 1;\">\r\n<div class=\"content_tab\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 30px 0px 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-size-adjust: none;\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-content-block\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 66px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-size-adjust: none;\">\r\n<div class=\"accordion style-2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-size-adjust: none;\">\r\n<div class=\"acc-panel\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-size-adjust: none;\">\r\n<div class=\"acc-body\" style=\"box-sizing: border-bo