order-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">Breakfast at your hotel at Cairo at First Residence and then met by your personal guide who will accompany you to Giza Plateau to visit one of the seven wonders of the ancient world,&nbsp;the Great Pyramids&nbsp;of Cheops, Chefren and Mykerinus, famous Sphinx and Valley temple facing the great statue. Visit to Solar Boat Museum at Pyramids area is included. Lunch will be served at a good quality local restaurant. Then transfer to enjoy&nbsp;the Egyptian Museum, which hosts the treasure room of the boy king Tutankhamun. Also there is the Mummification room for you to explore. Continue driving to Islamic Cairo, where you will be able to explore Khan El Khalili, Cairo&rsquo;s old bazaar. Back to your hotel.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"><strong>Meals: Breakfast, Lunch</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"full_itinerary_box\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid rgb(235, 235, 235); font-family: Avenir, sans-serif; border-radius: 10px; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253); float: left; width: 700px; position: relative; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n<div class=\"itinerary_title toggled\" id=\"itinerary_title_3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; float: left; width: 678px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"font-style:inherit\">Day 3: Fly Cairo to Luxor - Nile Cruise Tour</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"itinerary_desc\" id=\"itinerary_desc_3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -we