(48, 3, 93, 'Alf Leila Wa Leila Show Sharm El Sheikh', 'Enjoy an evening of stories from ‚ÄúAlf Leila Wa Leila‚Äù, known in English as ‚ÄúArabian Nights‚Äù. See stories and myths from Egyptian and Arabian history acted out and enjoy a seated meal.', '<p>enjoy a different night and attend Alf Leila Wa Leila Show (One Thousand and One Nights Show).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With each step you take ,you will reveal the secrets of the civilization, beauty and art all under one crown.The exquisite pharaonic and Bedouin live music performance demonstrates the precious legend about the history of the old ears along with the mind-blowing architecture which is great.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Also you will see the castle with its towers and domes that reflect the Islamic civilization.After that enjoy the Egyptian folklore, hours acrobats and the dancing fountain.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Then move to the oriental night Egyptian songs and oriental belly dancing.A moroccan dinner will be arranged before the show. Then transfer back to the hotel and overnight in Sharm.</p>', '14199436_1218062084924997_6439690556945798139_n.jpg', '10259797_998881320157743_3787832914069565037_n.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '40.00', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr;\"><span style=\"font-family:montserratregular; font-size:16px\">Pick up service from your hotel in Sharm &amp; return</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr;\"><span style=\"font-family:montserratregular; font-size:16px\">All transfers by air-conditioned deluxe vehicle</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr;\"><span style=\"font-family:montserratregular; font-size:16px\">Entrance fees to Alf Leila Wa Liela Show</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr;\"><span style=\"font-family:montserratregular; font-size:16px\">Dinner before the Show</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr;\"><span style=\"font-family:montserratregular; font-size:16px\">All service charges and taxes</span></div>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr;\"><span style=\"font-family:montserratregular; font-size:16px\">Any Extras not mentioned in the itinerary</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr;\"><span style=\"font-family:montserratregular; font-size:16px\">Tipping Kittty</span></div>', NULL, 'no', '5', NULL, 'alf-leila-wa-leila-show-sharm-el-sheikh', NULL, NULL, '2019-08-30 13:03:26', '2019-09-03 11:22:51'),
