(62, 3, 94, 'MS Mayfair Nile Cruise', 'Experience true luxury in Egypt aboard the MS Mayfair Nile cruise sailing between Luxor and Aswan, where exceptional service is the standard on all of its 5 elegant decks. Enjoy tastefully decorated public spaces, a spacious sundeck for relaxation, and homey accommodations, all serviced by an attentive and friendly staff. Your trip on the Nile is sure to be memorable, not only for the impressive ruins that you will see but the comfort of your home along the way.', '<div class=\"cruise_iti_repeat\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid rgb(235, 235, 235); font-family: Avenir, sans-serif; border-radius: 10px; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253); float: left; width: 700px; position: relative; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n<div class=\"iten gray toggled\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-family:inherit\">4 Days - Aswan / Luxor</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:inherit\">Every Friday</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"iten_desc\" id=\"toHide715\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 10px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; clear: both; width: 610.188px;\">\r\n<div class=\"full_itinerary\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; width: 610.188px; float: left; list-style-type: none; counter-reset: div-counter 0;\">\r\n<div class=\"full_itinerary_box gray\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid rgb(235, 235, 235); font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit