(98, 3, 89, 'Sunset Quad Bike Safari Tour in Luxor', 'Sunset Quad Bike Safari Tour in Luxor', '<p style=\"direction: ltr; \"><strong>From the moment your tour starts, your&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 255)\">Signature Tours Egypt</span><strong> guide will give you full attention. Once in the car, your guide will talk to you about all the things on the way as well as other aspects of your tour that will interest you.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"direction: ltr;\"><strong>Arrival at&nbsp;the quad bike station to ride your quad bike ATV in Luxor (very easy controls system even a casual rider can drive it with great convenience) to enjoy a unique safari excursion through the breathtaking scenery of the ancient land of the Pharaohs in the West bank of the River Nile in Luxor passing by the ancient monuments as well as modern Egyptian life and local people.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"direction: ltr;\"><strong>Go quad biking into the desert. Enjoy watching the sunset view at the desert of Luxor. On the way back to the quad bike station you will have fun on the sand dunes.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"direction: ltr; \"><strong>Travel in comfort back to your hotel, Luxor&nbsp;has so much to see, feel, eat and buy so if you have time and want to add more to your itinerary &ndash; just let us know what you are interested in and we will arrange it for you.</strong></p>', '69076378_10217140089565589_4392506497213399040_n.jpg', '69793296_2356108887800386_4412234420170260480_n.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '45.00', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr;\"><span style=\"font-family:montserratregular; font-size:16px\">Bedouin Safari excursion</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr;\"><span style=\"font-family:montserratregular; font-size:16px\">Bedouin guide</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr;\"><span style=\"font-family:montserratregular; font-size:16px\">Entrance fees and taxes</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: lt