(103, 3, 91, '13 Days Cairo, Nile Cruise & Red Sea Vacation', 'Spend a unique luxury vacation discovering fascinating Egypt. Start your trip in Cairo, and visit the most popular sites. Then fly to upper Egypt to enjoy sailing on the Oberoi Philae Nile Cruise visiting Aswan and Luxor before moving to relax on the beach of the Oberoi Sahl Hasheesh resort at the Red Sea.', '<div class=\"full_itinerary_box\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid rgb(235, 235, 235); font-family: Avenir, sans-serif; border-radius: 10px; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253); float: left; width: 700px; position: relative; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n<div class=\"itinerary_title toggled\" id=\"itinerary_title_1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; float: left; width: 678px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"direction: ltr; font-style: inherit;\">Day 1: Arrival Cairo - Welcome to land of the Pharaoh&rsquo;s</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"itinerary_desc\" id=\"itinerary_desc_1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 34px 20px; padding: 20px 0px 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: rgb(225, 225, 225); border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 15px;\">\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr;\"><span style=\"font-family:inherit\">Welcome to Cairo, Egypt (Around The Clock).</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr;\"><span style=\"font-family:inherit\">Your&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 255); font-family:inherit\">Signature</span><span style=\"font-family:inherit\">&nbsp;tour manager will meet and assist you at Cairo International Airport and provide Entry Visa for Egypt and then he will escort you to the Four Seasons Hotel Cairo at First Residence by exclusive air-conditioned deluxe vehicle. At your hotel the tour manager will assist with a smooth check-in and review your holiday itinerary with you to establish and confirm pick-up times for each tour. Overnight in Cairo at Four Seasons Hotel Cairo at First Residence.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"><strong>Welcome Drink</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"full_itinerary_box\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid rgb(235, 235, 235); font-family: Avenir, sans-serif; border-radius: 10px; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253); float: left; width: 700px; position: relative; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n<div class=\"itinerary_title toggled\" id=\"itinerary_title_2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; float: left; width: 678px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"direction: ltr; font-style: inherit;\">Day 2: Cairo Pyramids and Museum</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"itinerary_desc\" id=\"itinerary_desc_2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 34px 20px; padding: 20px 0px 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: rgb(225, 225, 225); border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 15px;\">\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">our private <span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 255)\">Signature Tours Egypt</span>&nbsp;Tour Guide and driver will accompany you to visit the famous Giza<a href=\"https://www.memphistours.com/Egypt/Egypt-Wikis/Egypt-Pyramids/wiki/Giza-Necropolis\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(8, 149, 255); text-decoration-line: none !important;\">&nbsp;</a>Plateau, home of Egypt&rsquo;s signature attractions to visit the Great Pyramids, one of the Seven Wonders of the ancient world including the Great Pyramid of Cheops, Middle pyramids of</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">Khephren, the smallest Pyramid of Mykerinos and the mysterious Sphinx, (the Father of Terror for the ancient Pharaohs). The tour includes a visit to the Valley Temple facing the great Sphinx. Following this, you will be transferred to visit the world-renowned Museum of Egyptian<a href=\"https://www.memphistours.com/Egypt/Egypt-Wikis/Cairo-Attractions/wiki/Egyptian-Museum-Cairo\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(8, 149, 255); text-decoration-line: none !important;\">&nbsp;</a>Antiques&nbsp;which exhibits a collection that now exceeds over 120000 masterpieces ranges from pre-dynastic era, Pharaonic era to the Greco- Roman period in Egypt. Then you will be transferred to your hotel in Cairo for an enjoyable overnight stay. Please note: There is an additional charge for entering the Pyramids and also the Solar Boat Museum. Please speak with your tour guide should you wish to purchase a ticket to enter one of these sites. Also an additional charge for the Mummies Room at the Egyptian Museum.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"><strong>Meals: Breakfast, Lunch</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"full_itinerary_box\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid rgb(235, 235, 235); font-family: Avenir, sans-serif; border-radius: 10px; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253); float: left; width: 700px; position: relative; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n<div class=\"itinerary_title toggled\" id=\"itinerary_title_3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; float: left; width: 678px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"direction: ltr; font-style: inherit;\">Day 3: Cairo Sightseeing</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"itinerary_desc\" id=\"itinerary_desc_3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 34px 20px; padding: 20px 0px 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: rgb(225, 225, 225); border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 15px;\">\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">After breakfast at your Hotel, your Tour Guide will collect you and escort you to the Old Citadel of Salah<a href=\"https://www.memphistours.com/Egypt/Egypt-Wikis/Cairo-Attractions/wiki/Salah-El-Din-Citadel\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(8, 149, 255); text-decoration-line: none !important;\">&nbsp;</a>El Din&nbsp;and Mohammed Ali Alabaster<a href=\"https://www.memphistours.com/Egypt/WikiTravel/Attractions-Cairo/wiki/Mohamed-Ali-Alabaster-Mosque\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(8, 149, 255); text-decoration-line: none !important;\">&nbsp;</a>Mosque&nbsp;which was designed and built in Turkish style and very similar to the Blue Mosque in Turkey.This magnificent structure is built at a very high point overlooking Old Cairo with spectacular views of the City as far as the Pyramids.It also hosts some very interesting Museums such as the Police, Military, Old Islamic Cairo, and old and modern history of Egypt. Finally, you will visit also the famous Khan El Khalili<a href=\"https://www.memphistours.com/Egypt/Egypt-Wikis/Cairo-Attractions/wiki/Khan-El-Khalili\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(8, 149, 255); text-decoration-line: none !important;\">&nbsp;</a>Bazaars&nbsp;and Open Market in Cairo. Overnight stay in Cairo.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"><strong>Meals: Breakfast, Lunch</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div cl