 solid; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: rgb(225, 225, 225); border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 15px;\">\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">6:00 a.m. to 7:00 a.m.Breakfast</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">07:00 a.m.Visit the Temple of Abydos</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">12.00 p.m.Sail to Luxor</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">12:30 p.m.Lunch</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">2:00 to 4:00 p.m.Free time for Spa</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">5:00 to 6:30 p.m.Visit Luxor Temple</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">8:00 p.m.Dinner</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">Overnight in Luxor</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"><strong>Meals: Breakfast, Lunch, Dinner</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"full_itinerary_box\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid rgb(235, 235, 235); font-family: Avenir, sans-serif; border-radius: 10px; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253); float: left; width: 700px; position: relative; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n<div class=\"itinerary_title toggled\" id=\"itinerary_title_10\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; float: left; width: 678px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"direction: ltr; font-style: inherit;\">Day 10: Luxor Nile Cruise - Transfer to Red Sea</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"itinerary_desc\" id=\"itinerary_desc_10\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 34px 20px; padding: 20px 0px 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: rgb(225, 225, 225); border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 15px;\">\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">After breakfast, you will be escorted by your Representative to an air conditioned vehicle for the short (approximately) 3 hour drive to Sahl Hashish, taking in the sights of the dry and sometimes mountainous landscape of the sand cliffs. On arrival at Sahl Hashish, you will check in to your luxury Oberoi Hotel in Resort for a relaxing day and evening. The Sahl Hasheesh Oberoi Hotel is in the best location for total relaxation,pampering and sheer luxury at this 5 star retreat. Only 30 minutes from Central Hurghada, it is close enough for day trips and adventures, yet at the same time a good distance away for peace and quiet. Quite literally, the Oberoi Sahl Hasheesh is one of Panorama Egypt Tours finest and newest partner Hotels with a wonderful record of guest satisfaction.Your deluxe hotel includes spa and fitness facilities along with swimming pool, sundecks and sea views. Overnight at your Hotel.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"><strong>Meals: Breakfast</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"full_itinerary_box\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid rgb(235, 235, 235); font-family: Avenir, sans-serif; border-radius: 10px; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253); float: left; width: 700px; position: relative; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n<div class=\"itinerary_title toggled\" id=\"itinerary_title_11\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; float: left; width: 678px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"direction: ltr; font-style: inherit;\">Day 11: Sahl Hashish Red Sea Optional Tours</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"itinerary_desc\" id=\"itinerary_desc_11\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 34px 20px; padding: 20px 0px 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: rgb(225, 225, 225); border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 15px;\">\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">A full day of relaxation at this peaceful upmarket resort with many things to do in and around the Hotel as well as optional tours. You can opt for diving and snorkeling experiences ( famous in the Red Sea), to canyon and cave adventures out in the sandy desert region. Jeep Safaris and Quad Biking tours are available during the daytime. A highly recommended evening excursion is into Hurghada to see the A Spectacular evening of Dance, Music, sound and lighting in this incredible and traditional evening of pure entertainment! Tonight you will go for amazing Arabian Night &lsquo;Alf Leila Wa Leila&rsquo; (means &lsquo;1001 Nights&rsquo;),in a unique setting of oriental architecture of colorful domes, high pillars and towers, huge gates, fountains, marble paths, and the never ending fantasy of Egyptian charm. An informative evening where you will discover more about the life of the Pharaohs and Bedouins, and also about customs and traditions of the region.Overnight at Hotel.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"><strong>Meals: Breakfast</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"full_itinerary_box\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid rgb(235, 235, 235); font-family: Avenir, sans-serif; border-radius: 10px; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253); float: left; width: 700px; position: relative; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n<div class=\"itinerary_title toggled\" id=\"itinerary_title_12\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; float: left; width: 678px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"direction: ltr; font-style: inherit;\">Day 12: Sahl Hashish Red Sea Optional Tours</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"itinerary_desc\" id=\"itinerary_desc_12\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 34px 20px; padding: 20px 0px 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: rgb(225, 225, 225); border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 15px;\">\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">Another full day after breakfast to enjoy your upmarket surroundings of Sahl Hashish with relaxtion or a further optional Tour. Overnight at your Hotel.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"><strong>Meals: Breakfast</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"full_itinerary_box\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid rgb(235, 235, 235); font-family: Avenir, sans-serif; border-radius: 10px; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253); float: left; width: 700px; position: relative; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n<div class=\"itinerary_title toggled\" id=\"itinerary_title_13\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 20px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; float: left; width: 678px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"direction: ltr; font-style: inherit;\">Day 13: Red Sea - Cairo Airport - Fly Back Home</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"itinerary_desc\" id=\"itinerary_desc_13\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 34px 20px; padding: 20px 0px 0px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: rgb(225, 225, 225); border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: 15px;\">\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">Last day to enjoy the sea resort scenery and prepare to transfer back to Cairo via Hurghada. You will be transferred to Hurghada Airport ( less than 30 Minutes) from Sahl Hashish by air conditioned vehicle then flown to Cairo International Airport where you will be escorted to the International Terminal for your flight home.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"><strong>Meals: Breakfast</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '123.jpg', '69078722_1676750222461418_44815836250112000_n.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '3150.00', '<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: left;\">Meet and greet service by our representatives at airports</li>\r\n	<li style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: left;\">Assistance of our guest relations during your stay</li>\r\n	<li style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: left;\">Entry Visa for Egypt provide upon arrival Cairo Airport</li>\r\n	<li style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: left;\">All airport transfer by private air-conditioned deluxe vehicle with Free WIFI</li>\r\n	<li style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: left;\">Transfer from Luxor to Hurghada by a private air-conditioned vehicle.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: left;\">Accommodation for 3 nights in the Four Seasons Hotel at the First Residence including daily breakfast.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: left;\">Accommodation for 6 nights on board Oberoi Philae Nile cruise on full board basis</li>\r\n	<li style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: left;\">Accommodation for 3 nights in the Oberoi Sahl Hasheesh Resort Hurghada including daily breakfast.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: left;\">Domestic flight Cairo/Aswan &ndash; Hurghada/Cairo</li>\r\n	<li style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: left;\">All sightseeing tours in Cairo - privately guided tours</li>\r\n	<li style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: left;\">All sightseeing tours on the cruise&nbsp;privately guided tours</li>\r\n	<li style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: left;\">All sightseeing tours in Cairo, Luxor, and Aswan as mentioned in the itinerary</li>\r\n	<li style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: left;\">Entrance fees to all sites as indicated on the itinerary.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: left;\">Local English-speaking tour guide during your tours</li>\r\n	<li style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: left;\">Cairo&nbsp;Nile Cruise&nbsp;&amp; Red Sea Vacation</li>\r\n	<li style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: left;\">Lunch at good quality local restaurant</li>\r\n	<li style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: left;\">Lunch at Naguib Mahfouz Restaurant in Cairo</li>\r\n	<li style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: left;\">Bottled water during your tours and transfers</li>\r\n	<li style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: left;\">Free wifi service during your stay in Egypt.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: left;\">All service charges and applicable taxes included</li>\r\n</ul>', '<div class=\"scroll_pane_new\" id=\"overview\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Avenir, sans-serif; width: 700px; float: left; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n<div class=\"program_box_data\" id=\"exclude\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; width: 700px; float: left;\">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: left;\">International Airfare</li>\r\n	<li style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: left;\">Any optional tours</li>\r\n	<li style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: left;\">Personal spending</li>\r\n	<li style=\"direction: ltr; text-align: left;\">Tipping Kitty</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"scroll_pane_new\" id